            "text": "How It Works"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "text": [
                "Using TCP Sockets/Server\n Can join chat room by entering a chat room name which will automatically connect you to the correct server and port number\n A third node/server will be in place where the chat rooms will be hosted\n  The server will act as a bridge between users in a chat room\n Chat room will stay open on the server as long as at least a single user is connected.\n  Saving processing power by not keeping rooms open indefinitely."
